With R_1=-22\text{ cm} = -R_2 and n_0=1.33 in Eq. , we get

	 \frac{1}{f} \amp = \left( \frac{n_l - n_0}{n_0}   \right)  \left(\frac{1}{R_1} - \frac{1}{R_2} \right)
	 \amp = \left( \frac{1.55 - 1.33}{1.33}   \right)  \times \frac{2}{-22}
	 \amp = -\frac{0.33}{22}

Therefore, f = 66.7\text{ cm}.
